p.d: In the fourth episode of the set, we visit the airport in Biala Podlaska. Here, one of the world's best aerobatic pilots – Maciej Pośpieszyński, is busy with his training. Our champion will show us the most spectacular displays of aerial and glider aerobatics and will advise us on how to learn to glide.
